flowchart LR
    Frontier[(URL Frontier<br/>per-domain priority queues)]
    Fetcher[Fetcher Pool<br/>async I/O]
    DNS[(DNS Cache)]
    Parser[HTML Parser]
    Filter[Content Filter<br/>SimHash dedup]
    Seen[(URL Seen<br/>Bloom + embedded KV)]
    Pages[(Page Archive<br/>object store)]

    Frontier -->|next URL| Fetcher
    Fetcher <-->|resolve| DNS
    Fetcher -->|html| Parser
    Parser -->|content| Filter
    Parser -->|extracted links| Seen
    Seen -.->|new URLs| Frontier
    Filter -->|store page| Pages

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Fetcher,Parser,Filter service
    class Frontier,DNS,Seen,Pages store
